<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="to-the-point">to the point</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>中肯的；切题的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Your advice is very much to the point.
你的建议很中肯。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wish you’d <strong>get to the point</strong> (= talk about the most important thing).
我希望你能切入正题。</p></div></div>